<h1 align="center">ğŸ”¬ AFusion: AlphaFold 3 GUI</h1>

<p align="center">
    <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.10-blue.svg">
    <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Framework-Streamlit-green.svg">
